channel.title: [Un-Continued]NotoriouzScape 508
channel.description:
[b]Not Releasing due to some people.[/b]
Here are some features that i was suppose to release with source.. [b] |NPC Training| |20 Executive PKing & General Stores| |NPC Chat & Dialogue| |Player Commands| |100% Barrow Tunnels| |Almost all Special Attacks| |99% Accurate Mapdata| |Proper item placement| |Rune C'bow Projectile finished & Real Dark Bow Special| |Working & Drainable Crystal Bow| |Working Saradomin Brew's| |Custom Quest's to use Godswords| |Good Economy| |Thieving works| |And more| [/b]
Stuff that arent done. [i] Pest Control [80%] ~ Now with [b]Working[/b] interfaces! Fishing Trawler [50%] ~ Still declaring some voids Jad [70%] ~ 40 Waves done and still teaching the Aggression on some NPC's Warrior Guild [90%] ~ Declaring some Voids Random Events [99%] ~ OMG 1 MORE EVENT AND A **** LOAD OF INTERFACES TO PUT!!! Castle Wars [70%] ~ Teaching and Adding my own timers.. Still examing the regular rs timers tho. Bounty Hunter [80%] ~ Not those crappy ones you see on some servers, The player actually walks through the cave thing and appears out the door instead of the teleport gfx. Also i added the arrows gfx above the target you are hunting so :D!!!! i feel accomplished on this. Fight Caves [50%] ~ Not happy about the timers i set. Takes too long for match to start. Agility [80%] ~ Almost like RS.. but some objects dont work properly Summoning [20%] ~ You can create pouch with the pouch interface now, except im trying to fix the "Dwarf Remains" thing on the summoning tab and teaching the summoned npc to follow and work with scrolls (e.g. "howl scroll") Farming [90%] ~ Works fine but sometimes it could jam up the players interface on vinesweeper. [/i] & No im not releasing this anymore because i've changed my mind due to some people. PC : [IMG]http://i41.tinypic.com/10nesyd.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2zgi8lz.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i40.tinypic.com/2n9bpd.jpg[/img]
Sorry , not releasing. But if you really want it send me a pm and why you want it. :\
